<br>
So, say you want to move around to the right of a creature.  Right-click and hold, press your right arrow button.. then as you slide to your right.. move your mouse to the left... so you are still looking at the monster.  If it is a large mob, then just strafe more then you turn... if it's a small, you can turn sharper to get around it quicker.<br>
<br>
